targets.query: SELECT sum("activesessions") AS "Active", sum("idlesessions") AS "Idle", sum("disconnectedsessions") AS "Disconnected", sum("othersessions") AS "Other", sum("ActiveSessions") AS "Active", sum("IdleSessions") AS "Idle", sum("DisconnectedSessions") AS "Disconnected", sum("OtherSessions") AS "Other" FROM "XdWorker" WHERE ("Host" = '172.30.190.73' OR "Host" = '172.30.190.74' OR "host" = '172.30.190.73' OR "host" = '172.30.190.74') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5m) fill(none)

SELECT sum("totalsessions") AS "Total" FROM "XdWorker" WHERE ("Host" = '172.30.190.73' OR "Host" = '172.30.190.74' OR "host" = '172.30.190.73' OR "host" = '172.30.190.74') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5m) fill(none)

SELECT sum("totalsessions") AS "Total" FROM "XdWorker" WHERE ("sitename" = 'AR_PROD' AND "deliverygroupname" = 'PRD_SCM163' OR "deliverygroupname" = 'PRD_SCM163_EDBOARD' OR "deliverygroupname" = 'PRD_SCM163_GLD') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5m) fill(none)
